OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FHelen Ford went to meet Matt Smith,
OL,8,Fwho has suffered from migraines since
OL,9,Fhe was 16
OL,11,FA man who has suffered debilitating
OL,12,Fmigraine attacks for 20 years hopes a
OL,13,Fnew drug could finally help alleviate
OL,14,Fhis pain.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
