OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FMatt Smith, from North Tyneside, told
OL,8,FITV Tyne Tees he had given up on
OL,9,Fgetting medication for migraine
OL,10,Fattacks which at times have been so
OL,11,Fbad he lost vision in both eyes and
OL,12,Frecovery took up to a week due to slow-
OL,13,Fto-subside facial pain.
OL,15,FA new treatment, which could become
OL,16,Favailable on the NHS, could be a light
OL,17,Fat the end of the tunnel for the 35-
OL,18,Fyear-old.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
