OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FThe new drug Atogepant - sold under
OL,8,Fthe brand name Aquipta and made by
OL,9,FAbbVie - has been given the green
OL,10,Flight for NHS use under new final
OL,11,Fdraft guidance from the National
OL,12,FInstitute for Health and Care
OL,13,FExcellence (Nice).
OL,15,FThe once-a-day tablet could only be
OL,16,Fprescribed by specialists and for
OL,17,Fpeople who have unsuccessfully tried
OL,18,Fat least three other treatments for
OL,19,Fmigraines.
