OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FMatt, who has suffered from migraine
OL,8,Fattacks since he was 16, described the
OL,9,Fcondition as a "continuous grind".
OL,11,F"It's quite a debilitating condition
OL,12,Fand a lonely condition," he said.
OL,13,F"It's something that is always there
OL,14,Fand is always in the background and as
OL,15,Fyou go through trying to live your
OL,16,Flife...it gives you almost a constant
OL,17,Fbattle with yourself in terms of being
OL,18,Fable to function at a level that you
OL,19,Fwould like to."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
