OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FMatt's attacks peaked during the
OL,8,Fpandemic, when he was experiencing
OL,9,Fthem for up to 20 days a month.
OL,11,FHe tried several treatments but -
OL,12,Fbecause some were originally intended
OL,13,Ffor other conditions - he found the
OL,14,Fside effects debilitating.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
