OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FThe condition can be severe and can
OL,8,Fimpact sufferers' ability to work,
OL,9,Fsocialise and care for dependents, and
OL,10,Fcan take a toll on their mental health.
OL,12,FThe new treatment would only be
OL,13,Favailable to people who have at least
OL,14,Ffour migraine days each month and have
OL,15,Ftried at least three other treatments
OL,16,F- offering a new choice for an
OL,17,Festimated 170,000 patients in England.
