OL,3,C'Migraine can be lonely and
OL,4,Cdebilitating but new drug gives me
OL,5,Chope'
OL,7,FMatt said: "It would give people hope
OL,8,Fin terms of having something specific
OL,9,Ffor the condition. It's meant to
OL,10,Ftackle symptoms and causes people have.
OL,12,F"People do struggle with this daily.
OL,13,FThere's no scope to be able to say I
OL,14,Fcan't work for that many hours or days
OL,15,Fin a week. A lot of people have to
OL,16,Fgrin and bear it. it's quite well
OL,17,Fhidden - you can struggle in silence.
OL,19,F"If it can help people live in a bit
OL,20,Fmore comfort and not having severe
OL,21,Fpain that's fantastic."
