OL,7,FWelcoming the new treatment, she told
OL,8,FITV News: "I raised this in parliament
OL,9,Frecently and the first parliamentary
OL,10,Fdebate on migraine since the 1960s
OL,11,Fwhich in itself is kind of baffling.
OL,13,F"I'm going to be discussing this with
OL,14,Fthe minister to see how we can get
OL,15,Fthese drugs to people faster because
OL,16,Fso many people who do access them say
OL,17,Fthey can be life changing."
