OL,7,FIf there are no appeals against its
OL,8,Ffinal draft guidance, Nice is expected
OL,9,Fto publish its final guidance on the
OL,10,Fdrug next month.
OL,12,FHealth Minister Andrew Stephenson
OL,13,Fsaid: "Migraines affect millions of
OL,14,Fpeople in this country and this new
OL,15,Ftreatment will help prevent recurring
OL,16,Fmigraine attacks when other medicines
OL,17,Fhave failed.
